'''长存湖'''([[拉丁文|拉丁文]]为"Lacus Perseverantia")是[[月球|月球]]上的一座小[[月海|月海]]，靠近[[危海|危海]]南端，最大尺寸72公里。1979年[[国际天文学联合会|国际天文学联合会]]正式接受了它的命名<ref name=gazetteer>{{cite web
 |url         = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3215
 |title       = Lacus Perseverantiae
 |work        = Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature
 |publisher   = International Astronomical Union (IAU) Working Group for Planetary System Nomenclature (WGPSN)
 |date        = 2010-10-18
 |accessdate  = 2015-06-17
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/68sundA4r?url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3215
 |archivedate = 2012-07-03
 |deadurl     = no
}}</ref>。

==位置和附近特征==
长存湖位于危海以南60-80公里处，处于危海盆地内靠外的区域<ref name=Wilhelms_1987_plate_4>{{cite book
 |work         = Plate 4A. Maria
 |title        = Geologic History of the Moon
 |url          = http://ser.sese.asu.edu/GHM
 |author       = Wilhelms D.
 |date         = 1987
 |series       = United States Geological Survey Professional Paper 1348
 |access-date  = 2016-04-19
 |archive-date = 2013-05-14
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20130514114936/http://ser.sese.asu.edu/GHM/ghm_04txt.pdf
 |dead-url     = yes
}}</ref>，月湖中心的[[月面坐标|月面坐标]]为{{Coord|7.8|N|61.9|E|globe:Moon}}<ref name=gazetteer/>。东南与直径60公里，已被[[熔岩|熔岩]]填塞的[[费尔米库斯陨石坑|费尔米库斯陨石坑]]接壤，二者被一条宽仅7公里的地带分开，接下来西北方是[[奥祖陨石坑|奥祖陨石坑]]和[[范阿尔巴达陨石坑|范阿尔巴达陨石坑]]；西南方则坐落着[[戴里陨石坑|戴里陨石坑]]和[[阿波罗尼奥斯陨石坑|阿波罗尼奥斯陨石坑]]；此外，月湖四周还散布着费尔米库斯陨坑和奥祖陨坑的一些卫星坑。以上是截止2015年月湖大部分表面中已命名的特征<ref>According to [http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov nomenclature guide МАС] {{Wayback|url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/ |date=20191205162958 }} ([http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/images/Lunar/lac_62_wac.pdf Map] {{Wayback|url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/images/Lunar/lac_62_wac.pdf |date=20190326175843 }}).</ref>。

==描述==
长存湖呈东北-西南向延伸，主要部分长约60公里，宽度由东到西为15至7公里不等；北端二条分支延伸长度为20公里，该湖最大尺寸有72公里。

在月湖中间横穿着一道朝向东北的山脊，山脊东部比西部略高<ref name=JMARS>According to the laser altimeter on the satellite [[月球勘测轨道飞行器|Lunar Reconnaissance Orbiter]], obtained through the program [http://jmars.asu.edu JMARS] {{Wayback|url=http://jmars.asu.edu/ |date=20190122103100 }}.</ref>；月湖中分布着一些小型(最多2公里)[[撞击坑|撞击坑]]，它们中最引人注目是出现有月球地幔特征的矿物
-[[橄榄石|橄榄石]]的存在。在月表上，它可能是由于[[小行星|小行星]]撞击或[[熔岩|熔岩]]喷发而形成<ref name=Powell_2012>{{cite journal
 |author       = Powell, K. E.; McGovern, P. J.; Kramer, G. Y.
 |title        = Olivine Detections at the Rim of Crisium Basin with Moon Mineralogy Mapper
 |journal      = 43rd Lunar and Planetary Science Conference, held March 19-23, 2012 at The Woodlands, Texas. LPI Contribution No. 1659, id.1689
 |date         = 2012
 |bibcode      = 2012LPI....43.1689P
 |url          = http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2012/pdf/1689.pdf
 |access-date  = 2016-04-19
 |archive-date = 2020-09-24
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20200924052406/https://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2012/pdf/1689.pdf
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>。

该月湖表面位于基准月面1.2-1.3公里以下(它的西北部[[月湾|月湾]]例外，这里的高度超出数百米)，较相邻被熔岩填塞的费尔米库斯陨石坑高0.6米，比邻近的[[危海|危海]]高2.4公里<ref name=JMARS/>。

